data.description: Step into your own private oasis with this stunning, all-brick ranch home nestled on a corner lot with a fully fenced yard. The meticulously landscaped yard boasts a captivating water feature, a covered patio for al fresco dining, and deck perfect for entertaining. Charming new front patio welcomes you in and sets the stage for the updates that lie within. Roof was replaced in 2020, HVAC 2019, Water heater 2021, Windows updated, Vapor barrier 2023, Owners suite bath and Kitchen renovated, added granite, stainless steel appliances, electric cooktop, new deck.    Situated on just under half an acre, this home offers the ideal balance of space and convenience, with downtown Raleigh a mere 5 minutes away. The list of upgrades is extensive, and a detailed inventory can be found in the document center for your perusal.    Don't miss the opportunity to make this dream home yours - schedule a showing today.
